---
title: Indian Stuffed Peppers Garam Masala-Spiced Chickpeas, Peas & Carrots
description: These sure ain't your Momma's stuffed peppers! We're changing it up big time with fragrant curry and garam masala. Garam masala, a vibrant spice mix of coriander, cinnamon, cadamom, and much more, infuses the filling with a bold indian flavor profile.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/552544846ced6edb5a8b4568.jpg
